Xavier Martin is a graduate of the University of Chicago (BA) and the ESC Bordeaux (Ecole Supérieure de Commerce de Bordeaux).  Mr. Martin has travelled widely in Eastern Europe, most recently in the Czech Republic, Poland, and Hungary for purposes of establishing a network of contacts for future sales activities. Mr. Martin is completely fluent in German and French (he is a native speaker of both languages); he also speaks English and understands Polish.